Microcontrolers:
--These are tiny computers that work exactly like desktops but lack keyboard, mouse and screen. 
--They give commands to the components, we attached with them, with precise timming.
--In short we can say that a coding language decide what to do while a microcontroller execute it.
--Microcontrolers are the basic that control the robot.
--Or we can say that if we have soul then machines have microcontrolers.
